// navigation stack via connecting to the navigationview::get-next-page signal,
// in that case the following shortcuts are supported:
//
// - <kbd>Alt</kbd>+<kbd>→</kbd>
//
// - Forward mouse button
//
// - Swipe/scrolling towards the left
//
